    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-04T18:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-12-04T18:35:00-05:00" n="540"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d540">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320.2 AA/11–851: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Embassy in Israel</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d540fn1">Drafted by Mr. <persName corresp="#p_WJA1"
                            >Waldo</persName>; cleared with <gloss target="#t_NEA1">NEA</gloss>,
                            <gloss target="#t_UNP1">UNP</gloss>, and <gloss target="#t_UNE1"
                            >UNE</gloss>; repeated to Beirut as <gloss target="#t_Unrap1"
                            >Unrap</gloss> 224 and to Paris as Gadel 339.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-12-04T18:35:00-05:00"
                            >December 4, 1951—6:35 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>410. View imminent implementation aid program to Israel Dept rep discussed
                    substance Leg Beirut desp no. 243 Nov 8<note n="2" xml:id="d540fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_924">p. 924</ref>.</note>
                    (copy of which available Emb) with Israel <gloss target="#t_Min1">Min</gloss>
                    Wash and urged that soon as aid program well under way possibly beginning New
                    Year Israel Govt undertake responsibility providing assistance for twenty
                    thousand Arabs and three thousand Jews in Israel still drawing <gloss
                        target="#t_PRA1">PRA</gloss> rations. Israel <gloss target="#t_Min1"
                        >Min</gloss> stated believed his govt wld agree this suggestion.</p>
                <p>Ur discretion suggest Emb take similar line with <gloss target="#t_FonOff1"
                        >FonOff</gloss>. Might wish indicate US supporting <persName
                        corresp="#p_BJB2">Blandford</persName>’s recommendations as principal
                    contributor Arab refugee program and light of substantial US aid to Israel for
                    refugee relief and resettlement projects.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_WJE1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
